OL,3,CPeople impacted by disorder urged to
OL,4,Capply for compensation
OL,6,FHomeowners and businesses who have
OL,7,Fbeen impacted by violent disorder in
OL,8,FHartlepool and Middlesbrough are being
OL,9,Furged to seek compensation.
OL,11,FCleveland's Police and Crime
OL,12,FCommissioner Matt Storey is
OL,13,Fencouraging people who suffered damage
OL,14,Fduring the unrest to contact their
OL,15,Finsurance companies.
OL,17,FOthers who were not insured, or did
OL,18,Fnot have adequate cover in place,
OL,19,Fcould be eligible to claim
OL,20,Fcompensation under the Riot
OL,21,FCompensation Scheme.
