OL,3,CPeople impacted by disorder urged to
OL,4,Capply for compensation
OL,6,FMatt Storey said: "I've spent time in
OL,7,Fboth Hartlepool and Middlesbrough
OL,8,Fsince the disorder earlier this month
OL,9,Fand it has been heartbreaking to see
OL,10,Fthe damage to homes, businesses and
OL,11,Fvehicles.
OL,13,F"People affected by this mindless
OL,14,Fvandalism should not be out of pocket
OL,15,Fand it's important that affected
OL,16,Fcommunities can seek the financial
OL,17,Fsupport they need.
