OL,3,CPeople impacted by disorder urged to
OL,4,Capply for compensation
OL,6,F"If your property was not insured or
OL,7,Fyour insurance company have refused
OL,8,Fcompensation, please submit a claim to
OL,9,Fsee if you are eligible for the Riot
OL,10,FCompensation Scheme.
OL,12,F"My team will be working closely with
OL,13,Flocal councils and community groups to
OL,14,Fshare information about the scheme, to
OL,15,Freach as many affected people as
OL,16,Fpossible."
