OL,3,CPeople impacted by disorder urged to
OL,4,Capply for compensation
OL,6,FTo qualify for compensation through
OL,7,Fthe Riot Compensation Scheme, victims
OL,8,Fmust be able to demonstrate that they
OL,9,Fsuffered damage or loss as a result of
OL,10,Fthe violent disorder which took place
OL,11,Fin Hartlepool on Wednesday 31 July and
OL,12,Fin Middlesbrough on Sunday 4 August.
OL,14,FApplications can only be made with a
OL,15,Fcrime reference number, provided once
OL,16,Fthe crime has been reported to the
OL,17,Fpolice.
OL,19,FThose who have insurance must claim
OL,20,Fthrough their insurer first.
