OL,4,Capply for compensation
OL,6,FApplicants will need to show evidence
OL,7,Fof the losses they are claiming in the
OL,8,Fform of receipts, bank statements,
OL,9,Fsurveyor's report or photographic
OL,10,Fevidence.
OL,12,FThe Riot Compensation Scheme does not
OL,13,Fcover personal items, loss of trade or
OL,14,Frent or personal injuries.
